{{ comp.hero({
  tagline: "Three ideas explain almost everything in NetScript.",
  subhead: "The contract is the source of truth, the host is empty until plugins fill it, and one runtime brings up many resources together. Hold these three and the rest of the docs read as detail.",
  ctas: [
