{{ comp callout { type: "note", title: "Still alpha" } }}
NetScript is in <strong>alpha</strong> on the path to beta (targeting late 2026). The published package surface is the contract: what you import from <code>jsr:@netscript/*</code> is what's documented and type-checked. Every <code>@netscript/*</code> package shares one aligned version (<code>{{ releaseVersion }}</code>) and releases move in lockstep. Scaffolded JSR imports use exact <code>{{ releaseSpecifier }}</code> pins for the alpha train. Build with us — but pin your versions.
{{ /comp }}

